                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">（幸福桥&nbsp;出门会被捏耳朵&nbsp;好像是祝福的意思）<br />
去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>肯定要去看天涯海角啦&nbsp;这个是有学生票的&nbsp;50元&nbsp;我们是自己去的&nbsp;有好几趟公交到的&nbsp;也比较好等&nbsp;这边的海虽然没有<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14786.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="蜈支洲岛" target="_blank">蜈支洲岛</a>那么清&nbsp;不过跟<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196343.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大东海" target="_blank">大东海</a>比较还是挺清的&nbsp;不过这边的沙子颗粒比较大&nbsp;不是那种细沙&nbsp;但是景区内是不让游泳的&nbsp;所以好可惜的&nbsp;进门有一个天涯海角星&nbsp;导游说要出来的时候拍照&nbsp;具体原因忘记啦&nbsp;下午出来的时候&nbsp;折射的太阳光&nbsp;很漂亮&nbsp;里面有原来2块钱后面的南天一柱&nbsp;之前以为天涯海角是在一块石头上&nbsp;后来才明白&nbsp;是2块&nbsp;一块天涯石&nbsp;一块海角石&nbsp;天涯石比较好找&nbsp;海角石在它后面&nbsp;比较偏&nbsp;可能太高啦&nbsp;字体也没重新刷&nbsp;不是很清晰&nbsp;刚开始都没看到&nbsp;南山寺之前看攻略好像还不错&nbsp;不过我没啥信仰&nbsp;对它也不敢兴趣&nbsp;就没去啦<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815937.html" data-pid="277815937">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B3/wKgBEFpHLnCAFLIxAAE9-15cgsQ76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815937" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">（拍照的人真的太多啦）<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815938.html" data-pid="277815938">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B3/wKgBEFpHLnCABo4dAADzi5xxI8U60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815938" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815939.html" data-pid="277815939">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B3/wKgBEFpHLnCAdaY2AAIrTDibu-U78.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815939" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">（清清的海水）<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815940.html" data-pid="277815940">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B3/wKgBEFpHLnCAdigTAAFrXffZ7ow81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815940" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">（天涯石&nbsp;海角石照的不清&nbsp;就不传啦&nbsp;）<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196343.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大东海" target="_blank">大东海</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16020.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚龙湾" target="_blank">亚龙湾</a>都是免费的海滩&nbsp;没事可以去逛逛&nbsp;不论是下午还是晚上&nbsp;逛着都挺惬意<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>那有个椰梦长廊<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196343.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大东海" target="_blank">大东海</a>的话&nbsp;沙滩吧比较多<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16020.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚龙湾" target="_blank">亚龙湾</a>就都是豪华酒店啦<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815941.html" data-pid="277815941">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B4/wKgBEFpHLnGAIB98AAFkET-rvUU54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815941" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">（<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>的椰梦长廊晚上好多广场舞&nbsp;唱歌的&nbsp;很热闹的）<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815942.html" data-pid="277815942">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B4/wKgBEFpHLnGALDmpAADoZnPTf7s85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815942" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815943.html" data-pid="277815943">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B4/wKgBEFpHLnGALymfAADFad1t7bM00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815943" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815944.html" data-pid="277815944">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B4/wKgBEFpHLnGALPdrAAD6V4vKg-c87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815944" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815945.html" data-pid="277815945">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B5/wKgBEFpHLnGAEpfMAAJR_YgErDM93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815945" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">（<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16020.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚龙湾" target="_blank">亚龙湾</a>的海&nbsp;这的沙子就比较细啦&nbsp;不过好多路口都被酒店给封啦&nbsp;我们走啦一会才发现一个口&nbsp;真是坑啊）<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>还有一些免费的景点&nbsp;我们去花海的时候就比较悲哀啊&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/24023.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="花都" target="_blank">花都</a>被别人采啦&nbsp;游客太自私啦&nbsp;从小就被教育不要摘&nbsp;看着他们还是每人一大把&nbsp;不想发表意见啦&nbsp;还有一些花谢啦&nbsp;铲掉啦&nbsp;就剩光光的土地啦&nbsp;感觉挺失望的<br />
海鲜当然是吃的首先啦。我们之前在网上各种游记和各种点评网站上各种看&nbsp;最后选了很有游记都推荐的第一市场的阿浪海鲜店<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815946.html" data-pid="277815946">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:449px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B5/wKgBEFpHLnGACM0mAAHThWkJavg28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815946" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">还挺好的&nbsp;正如网上所说，老板比较热情&nbsp;派人陪你去买海鲜&nbsp;如果你想吃什么就直接跟她说&nbsp;不知道的话&nbsp;让她给你推荐&nbsp;人都挺热情的&nbsp;还帮你砍价&nbsp;买的也挺新鲜的&nbsp;鲜榨的果汁也挺好喝的<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815947.html" data-pid="277815947">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:399px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B6/wKgBEFpHLnKATX43AAH9fh7od1s69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815947" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815948.html" data-pid="277815948">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F2/C4/wKgBZ1o3LCqAIG_-AAOQZRueMcI77.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815948" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815949.html" data-pid="277815949">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:600px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B6/wKgBEFpHLnKAP-5jAAKxHm3AfwQ00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815949" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815950.html" data-pid="277815950">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:567px;width:518px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/94/1E/wKgBZ1o2L82AanXVAAq80G4Xltw105.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815950" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815951.html" data-pid="277815951">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:613px;width:520px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s1/M00/03/90/wKgIC1pAm-6AbRP-AAw-zsBB8Wg961.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815951" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815952.html" data-pid="277815952">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:606px;width:517px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/84/B7/wKgBEFpHLnOAJba8AAvWMEEdH-o812.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815952" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8150162/277815953.html" data-pid="277815953">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:589px;width:508px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F5/FE/wKgBZ1o3L6-ADXRfAArqAEkbJIU107.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277815953" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">呜呜呜呜&nbsp;通过这次发现看攻略很有必要&nbsp;他们推荐的都真的很好吃啊&nbsp;必吃&nbsp;椰子饭&nbsp;芒果螺&nbsp;蛏子&nbsp;螃蟹<br />
做过费用的大概列表吧<br />
机票&nbsp;1000/人&nbsp;往返&nbsp;（我买的是打折的&nbsp;所以还是很便宜的）<br />
住宿&nbsp;150左右/天&nbsp;（这个是要看你们的要求啦）<br />
景点门票&nbsp;50/人（学生票）&nbsp;印象成人票是102/人&nbsp;好像具体忘记啦<br />
海鲜&nbsp;80-100/人<br />
我的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>之旅就这些啦&nbsp;希望你们的更精彩<br />
</p>
    
                        
